profile:
HVAC CleanPro provides heat pump cleaning and air quality testing for residential and commercial properties. We currently service all of New Brunswick, Canada.

The benefits of having your heat pump cleaned once a year include: Increased performance and efficiency, prolong the lifespan of your equipment, decreased health risk due to mold, cleaner air to breathe, decreased cost of your utility bills.

Book a heat pump cleaning and receive a FREE air quality test, valid for single family homes, apartments, businesses, and institutions.
